summary: Wooden bat to beat the hell out of people.
descriptionHtml:
==============================Description===============================
Wooden bat that you use to beat people up.
Does not do allot of damage,so more time to beat up your enemy.
Must have steel smithing to create it, not going to bother changing it as long as you can create it.
Can be created at any forge.


==============================Installation==============================

Extract to data folder and activate Knuppel.esp

==============================Other==============================
The damage seems fair for such a weapon,not going to put a insane amount on damage on it.
